{"tid":1655753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我阿公係以前係學唐代玄術，幫曼聯占左支卦","createTime":"2019-10-15T08:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:32:28.000Z","uid":243691,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"946f4fe5b1d25a3eef2465924c3f21c3fa945cf6","tid":1655753,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"佢話曼聯近依三年都唔會有起色<br />\n仲話曼聯本身有兩隻邪魔 <br />\n今年走左一隻 但之後會番番黎<br />\n仲話英超一山不能藏二虎<br />\n唔可以有兩隊紅色（紅色屬火，兩火會相沖）<br />\n近期既高潮最快都要去到十一月尾<br />\n因為十一月同曼聯好夾<br />\n即使差極都有個譜<br />\n信不信由你 依啲野信則有不信則冇<br />\n你唔信既唔該出番去 唔好係度盲反<br />\n我阿公學左玄學好多年<br />\n之前仲占中左利記一世都唔會拎到英超<br />\n好準"},{"pid":"e1e8c140d5f38ca472ff38a12d2e1aacb4186411","tid":1655753,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"我係泊大巴 你地有野再占可以搵我"},{"pid":"bcc8a4db3b331a5c79b838750ef4122fd9bde2d9","tid":1655753,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d393d0d77ef47381d840708ebe7df14148b487","tid":1655753,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"我利今季就攞英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4674cf442c74ffc1b3d3f6fbae855c82ef4c73c","tid":1655753,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32d393d0d77ef47381d840708ebe7df14148b487","tid":1655753,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"我利今季就攞英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"我阿公唔會錯"},{"pid":"cb001b5ff9bdfa6b0a810a78810c0820952980e8","tid":1655753,"uid":243691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0101d30a01a3f600d13fbed5ad7019fc9288ef"